After user types partial text Triggering service 
says that text is ready, 
Now Phrase generator is going to do beam search 
over the model generated results and it picks up 
top-k  results 

After it picking up top-k results this is going to 
do the following:

It applies the following criteria:
1. Remove long sentences 
2. Remove low confidence suggestions
Picks up the remaining words and chose the top one
